It could also belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category as it deals with recommendation systems, which are a common application of information retrieval techniques. 

The Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category is also a possibility as the paper proposes a method for building explainable recommendation systems, which is a common goal in AI research. 

The Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) category is a possibility as the paper deals with natural language explanations of recommendation systems. 

Finally, the Cybersecurity (cs.CY) category is a possibility as the paper deals with the security and privacy implications of recommendation systems, which is a common concern in cybersecurity research.
